## Root scripts
From repo root:
- `npm run dev:client` · `npm run dev:server` · `npm run lint` · `npm run build`
- `npm run env:local` · `npm run env:cloud -- --ref <project-ref>` · `npm run env:push-vercel -- --client-project ... --server-project ...`

## Deploy model
- Production **client**: branch **`master-client`** (or Vercel project root `client`).
- Production **server**: branch **`master-server`** (or Vercel project root `server`).
- Integration: **`main`** / **`master`** + `ci.yml` (lint + build, no deploy).
